{"tid":516991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來肥婆無羞恥心係真","createTime":"2018-01-02T01:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T16:51:05.000Z","uid":128221,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ac81a083f12de9f3ea019d57f85257888d0ae6","tid":516991,"uid":128221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:21:55.000Z","msg":"今朝坐巴士，入面個乘客落左車，個肥婆想坐入去，咁我成個身90度轉左，俾佢行入去，點知佢大大聲話：入唔到喎！<br />\n我望左望，我對腳係完全離開哂，無block到佢要行入去既路,所以我應佢:我對腳係哂出面啦。<br />\n<br />\n佢藐嘴藐舌咁入去，坐低左之後又係咁藐我'接'我，又間唔中專登勁大動作郁下，扮哂俾我逼親。<br />\n<br />\n大佬，睇身型都知邊個逼邊個啦，落車唔該無聲，老奉要讓佢，行嗰陣仲要專登撞落你到，一路'接接接'，落左車都要睥住你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講真有禮貌少少，成個人企出黎俾佢入左先坐都得。<br />\n<br />\n真心唔明因爲自己既身型搞到人仲可以發人脾氣，肥係咪會改變地人地道德觀念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82a08c7678bd485bc2a33d6f5fc00d99011d1316","tid":516991,"uid":83094,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d2e2c8cdcd4bc598adb3fee1ae0325a5f85a053","tid":516991,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82a08c7678bd485bc2a33d6f5fc00d99011d1316","tid":516991,"uid":83094,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"衰婆我永遠照顧你"},{"pid":"6bb3edf59107c3b9b0aaf5e147e745cf0587e154","tid":516991,"uid":85880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T04:20:18.000Z","msg":"其實肥婆句 「入唔到喎。」<br />\n 係有弦外之音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4cc847dfe66dc853ad7f7a8b684c58e7c90200","tid":516991,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bb3edf59107c3b9b0aaf5e147e745cf0587e154","tid":516991,"uid":85880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-